'''顾雅明'''（{{lang-en|Peter Ah-Ming Koo}}, {{bd|1952年|9月5日||}}）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ourcampaigns.com/CandidateDetail.html?CandidateID=190464|title=Our Campaigns - Candidate - Peter Koo|website=www.ourcampaigns.com|access-date=July 10, 2018}}</ref>是一位美国华裔政治人物，[[纽约市议会|纽约市议会]]第20选区市议员。

==生平==
1952年出生于[[中国|中国]][[上海|上海]]，后搬迁至[[英属香港|英属香港]]，1971年移民至[[美国|美国]]，1975年毕业于[[新墨西哥大学|新墨西哥大学]]药学院，靠在[[肯德基|肯德基]]和[[唐恩都乐|唐恩都乐]]赚取最低工资支付学费。后成为[[药剂师|药剂师]]有五家药品连锁店。<ref name="Mimoni">{{cite news|url=http://www.queenscourier.com/articles/2008/03/12/news/regional/northeast/news08.txt|title=Community activist Peter Koo challenges Stavisky|publisher=The Queens Courier|author=Victor G. Mimoni|date=March 12, 2008|accessdate=November 20, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716022117/http://www.queenscourier.com/articles/2008/03/12/news/regional/northeast/news08.txt|archive-date=July 16, 2011|url-status=dead}}</ref>2010年1月1日当选[[纽约市议会|纽约市议会]]第20选区市议员。<ref name="Rhoades">{{cite news|url=http://www.zwire.com/site/news.cfm?newsid=20383288&BRD=2731&PAG=461&dept_id=574902&rfi=6|title=Can Republican Koo beat Flushing Dem?|author=Liz Rhoades|publisher=[[Queens_Chronicle|Queens Chronicle]]|date=October 29, 2009|accessdate=November 20, 2009}}{{Dead link|date=May 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dnainfo.com/new-york/20120123/flushing/queens-city-councilman-peter-koo-defects-democrats |title=Queens City Councilman Peter Koo Defects to Democrats |work=DNAinfo |date=January 23, 2012 |accessdate=September 24, 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925144337/http://www.dnainfo.com/new-york/20120123/flushing/queens-city-councilman-peter-koo-defects-democrats |archivedate=September 25, 2015 }}</ref>2012年将政党从[[美国共和党|美国共和党]]转向[[美国民主党|美国民主党]]。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/queens/city-councilman-peter-koo-flushing-defect-democratic-party-article-1.1009456 | location=New York | work=Daily News | title=Queens Councilman Peter Koo flips from Republican to Democrat | first=Lisa L. | last=Colangelo | date=January 23, 2012}}</ref>

==家庭==
顧雅明與程麗珍（Bernadette Ching Koo）結縭，共育有1子1女。兒子為顧崇輝（Timothy Koo）<ref name="紐約市議會"/><ref name="世界日報2009"/>，1984年出生<ref name="顧雅明傳">{{Cite book |title=顾雅明传: 从新移民到市议员 |author1=邱辛晔 |author2=罗慰年|author3=黄永钢|author4=沈新德
|publisher=易文出版社 |date=2017 |isbn=978-1-9407-4200-7}}</ref>{{rp|46}}；女兒為顧安婷（Tiffany Koo）<ref name="紐約市議會"/><ref name="世界日報2009"/>，1986年出生<ref name="顧雅明傳"/>。

